# TextRenderSystem  (sbx)

## Purpose
Render bridge for world-space text: sole adder of DrawStringInFrameEvent. Returns early until the
ResourceMapSingletonComponent is present. Each frame it resolves every LabelComponent's font id
against the resource map's font map and emits one draw event per label (transform, text, font,
colour, kerning, line spacing). Labels whose font id is not in the map are skipped.

## Input Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| ResourceMapSingletonComponent | read | Resolves font ids to fonts; guard (returns early if absent) |
| LabelComponent | read | One draw event emitted per label with a resolvable font |

## Output Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| DrawStringInFrameEvent | add (inframe) | One per drawable label; consumed by Renderer2DSystem this frame |
